      <title>韩国加强监管 严厉打击加密货币交易欺诈行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-korea-hunts-for-fraudulent-crypto-trading-as-rules-tighten</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国监管机构正在加大对当地加密货币交易所的压力，要求其根除可疑交易，这是本月晚些时候生效的新数字资产法旨在加强投资者保护的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-korea-hunts-for-fraudulent-crypto-trading-as-rules-tighten</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆汽车业务在华增长，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/continental-shares-jump-as-auto-unit-sees-growth-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆汽车集团表示其汽车部门在华业务的强劲增长将有助于抵消欧洲需求低迷的影响，随后该公司股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/continental-shares-jump-as-auto-unit-sees-growth-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行将其德国消费金融业务出售给 Bawag</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/barclays-sells-its-german-consumer-finance-business-to-bawag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行同意将其德国消费金融业务出售给 Bawag Group AG，这是该英国银行业巨头简化其跨业务线和跨地区布局的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/barclays-sells-its-german-consumer-finance-business-to-bawag</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:12:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
