      <title>美国就业报告显示 6 月份招聘大幅放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/us-jobs-report-to-show-a-substantial-slowdown-in-hiring-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预测人士预计，美国就业月度报告将显示六月份招聘人数下降，同时工资增长也将放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/us-jobs-report-to-show-a-substantial-slowdown-in-hiring-in-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
